#

Ambrosia Apple Delight

5 min
$4.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeVegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack/Dessert

Tags:

QuickHealthySnack

Description

A refreshing blend of sweet ambrosia apple slices with creamy Greek yogurt and a drizzle of honey, perfect for a quick snack or a light dessert.

Ingredients

  • ambrosia apple: 1 large
  • greek yogurt: 1 cup
  • honey: 2 tablespoons
